# cylinder side wall + annular floor + plug: ONE wall fix — LIGGGHTS 3.8
# supports a single wall/gran of style mesh, so the plug cannot get its own
# (first smoke run failed on exactly that). The orifice opens by MOVING the
# plug down out of the flow (fix move/mesh, the aor.in lift pattern) and
# parking it below the counting plane.
